	<h1 class="title">过了好几个月，《蚁人》和《头脑特工队》终于要来中国了</h1>
	<div class="author-date clearfix">					
			<div class="author clearfix">
					<span class="avatar x25 circle">
						<img src="/system/users/faces/102277/small/102277.jpg?1432868256" alt="">
					</span>
				<span class="name">韩方航 </span>
			</div>
		<span class="date smart-date" data-originDate="2015-09-25 09:26:29 +0800"></span>
	</div>
	<div class="banner">
			<img src="/system/articles/articleshows/15532/medium/15532.jpeg?1443106557" alt="" />			
	</div>
